 family. I=E2=80=99m very grateful that I get to work with my brother and p=
roud of everything he=E2=80=99s doing (HUGE day yesterday despite being att=
acked by an unscrupulous competitor [ https://substack.com/redirect/6de3d1d=
9-49ee-41c1-99b6-8acae07bad07?j=3DeyJ1IjoiOXAwZ3QifQ.gb8J5T7GnA_ZlNuaMZjmlX=
XepKbqOsa8-6m8ExkRNpU ]), and this is as good an overview of Dan=E2=80=99s =
world as there is.=20
